dc_title_s: Geologic map of the Alcalde Hills quadrangle, Fresno County, California
dc_description_s: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. "Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle Alcalde Hills, CA 1969. Photoinspected 1978. DMA 1856 III NW- series V895." "First printing, March 2007." "Brian Pitts honorary map." Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology, most recent 1969. Includes "pertinent references", most recent 1972.
dc_publisher_s: Santa Barbara Museum of Natural History
